Package edu.ucsc.cross.hse.core.variable

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Variable<X>
    An interface that is used to implement structures that are capable of doing different things using pointer protection.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DependentVariable<P>
    A value whose value is dependent on another value.
    DynamicVariable<X>
    A variable that will link with a field of another object and maintain access to the most current value of that field.
    RandomVariable
    A random double variable with it's value always generated at random based on the range provided Intended Operator: User
